snippet.title: Live Coding: Learning Rust from scratch
snippet.description:
Today we will explore the Rust programming language. I don't have any experience with Rust so we will start at the very beginning with learning how to do a Hello World. We will work on building a cookbook with some basic reference code for future use.

Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon
